'''Martin Khor''' ([[1951]] - ): Umuyobozi w’[[Ihuriro ry Ibihugu Bikiri mu Nzira y’Amajyambere]] (''Third Word Network'') aharanira kuvugira ibihugu bikennye avuga ko amategeko agenga ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga ari inzititizi ku bukungu bw’ibihugu bikennye. Akomeza avuga ko amategeko yose aza arengera ibihugu bikize kurusha ibihugu bikennye.

